longBusinessSummary: Nexen Corporation manufactures and sells rubber products in South Korea. The company offers tubes and flaps, solid tires, carbon masterbatch pellets and sheets, golf balls, and bladders for tires. It also provides logistics services, including sea, bulk, air, inland transport and distribution, warehouse, and knock down. The company also exports and distributes its products to approximately 140 countries. Nexen Corporation was founded in 1968 and is headquartered in Gimhae, South Korea.
